dct_title_s: Position of the English and French fleets immediately previous to the action on the 5th, Sepr. 1781
dct_description_sm: engraved for Stedmans History of the American war.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows Lynn Haven Bay and mouth of Chesapeake Bay.
"Engraved for Stedmans History of the American War." in lower center.
